metadata.name: "acopyofacopyofacopyofa..." clone#02
metadata.description:
unique AI portrait Art series by Lars Nagler
3500 x 3500 pixel jpeg

-
this series is a reflection from the book "Never Let Me Go" by K. Ishiguro

in simple terms, it is about clones that exist only to donate vital organs to the original later. 
we see clones without an identity of their own, trapped in time partitions whose duration they do not know and which do not allow them any enjoyment of life. 

they are "on hold" - for someone else.
